The Expert’s Choice.

00:00:54.760 --> 00:00:56.679
Vsauce!

00:00:56.679 --> 00:01:00.510
Kevin here.

00:01:00.510 --> 00:01:05.790
With a 34-year-old computer that took me three
weeks, 30 emails with three vintage computer

00:01:05.790 --> 00:01:12.050
experts and a special request from an eBay
store exclusively dedicated to selling old

00:01:12.050 --> 00:01:16.110
